  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- in town, it was-- it was serious economically because they-- those who joined the party, of course, would not buy in a Jewish store.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- and in as much as the major employers, the-- both Odin [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Verka ?] and those who supported this major store were dominated by the Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did not do business with Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it-- it was-- it was an important element of daily life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That thought did not occur to them because in the Weimar Republic, the-- the instability of the-- of national politics was such that we were sure very much in the spirit of my father's bet that parties like the Nazis would come and go and we just had to sit and-- and be patient and they would be sure to go.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After Hitler had been in-- in power for a-- a few-- a few months, we knew it was very serious.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not per se.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, elections were-- dominated the-- the whole atmosphere, very much as a presidential election does here, except that elections of various types happened a little more often in Germany.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The Jews in-- in the Weimar Republic were very much part and parcel of civic life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no exclusion that I was aware of.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think they were very proud of the fact that they were full citizens.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
